    <title>JavaScript入門 - 第2回 詳細解説</title>
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .text-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .preview-area {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100px;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
